---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About EOB Decoder" description="EOB Decoder is a free consumer tool that helps US patients understand and dispute medical bills. Learn about our mission and tools.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F7B8C 0%, #2D4A7A 100%);" class="text-white py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-bold mb-4 leading-tight" style="font-size: 40px;">About EOB Decoder</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-100" style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6;">A free tool for US patients who are tired of confusing medical bills.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-slate">

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-0 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">Medical billing in the United States is needlessly complex. Patients regularly receive confusing Explanation of Benefits (EOB) documents they can't decipher, bills that contain errors they don't know how to challenge, and correspondence from insurers written in opaque jargon. EOB Decoder exists to level the playing field — giving ordinary patients the information and tools they need to understand, question, and dispute their bills.</p>

      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">Studies show that up to 80% of medical bills contain errors, and the average overcharge on a hospital stay exceeds $1,000. Most patients never dispute these charges because they don't know how. EOB Decoder helps change that.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Our Tools</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
        <div class="bg-white border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mb-2" style="font-size: 18px;">
            <a href="/eob-decoder" class="text-[#0F7B8C] hover:underline">EOB Decoder</a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[#334155] text-sm leading-relaxed">Paste in the text from your Explanation of Benefits document and get a plain-English breakdown of what it means — what your insurance paid, what you owe, and why. Powered by AI and free to use.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mb-2" style="font-size: 18px;">
            <a href="/dispute-letter" class="text-[#0F7B8C] hover:underline">Dispute Letter Generator</a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[#334155] text-sm leading-relaxed">Generate a professional dispute letter to send to your insurer or provider. Fill in the details of your situation and get a clear, well-structured letter ready to send.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mb-2" style="font-size: 18px;">
            <a href="/billing-errors" class="text-[#0F7B8C] hover:underline">Billing Error Checklist</a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[#334155] text-sm leading-relaxed">Work through a comprehensive checklist of the most common medical billing errors. Identify specific problems on your bill so you know exactly what to dispute.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Who Built This</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">EOB Decoder is built and maintained by an independent developer. It is not affiliated with any insurance company, hospital system, or healthcare provider. We have no financial relationship with any party involved in medical billing.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">A Note on Our Tools</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">Our tools use AI to help you understand your bills and draft disputes. They are for informational purposes only and are not a substitute for legal or professional advice. For complex disputes — especially those involving large sums or potential legal action — we recommend consulting a licensed healthcare advocate or attorney.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Get in Touch</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">Questions, feedback, or ideas? We'd love to hear from you. Email us at <a href="mailto:amitsharma00261@gmail.com" class="text-[#0F7B8C] hover:underline">amitsharma00261@gmail.com</a> or visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-[#0F7B8C] hover:underline">Contact page</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
